components.html: I. Interconnectedness with Group or Affiliated Companies or Other Related Parties
components.label: Content

components.html:
1 Please indicate if the Licensed Corporation has the following off-balance sheet financial arrangementNote with group or affiliated companies or other related parties.
(Please choose all options that are applicable to the Licensed Corporation.) [BQ17011]
components.label: Content

components.html: Note: Excluding expense reimbursement arrangements.
components.label: Content
(a) Provide guarantee for the banking facilities in favour of group or affiliated companies or other related parties

(b) Pledge its assets (eg, marketable securities, unquoted shares, deposit, land and building provided by the Licensed Corporation) to secure banking facilities in favour of group or affiliated companies or other related parties
(c) Pledge or repledge its client securities/ securities collaterals to secure banking facilities in favour of group or affiliated companies or other related parties
(d) Other off-balance sheet financial arrangements, please specify:
(e) N/A - the Licensed Corporation does not have any off-balance sheet financial arrangement with group or affiliated companies or other related parties.

components.html: 2 (a) Is the Licensed Corporation aware of any of its substantial shareholder(s) which is/ are under financial distress (eg, has net liabilities, fails to repay overdue loans or debts, subject to winding-up petition, under receivership) ? [BQ17011A_01]
components.label: Content

components.html: 2 (b) If the answer is "Yes" in (a),
components.label: Content

components.html: (i) Please state the name(s) of the substantial shareholder(s) which is/ are under financial distress. [BQ17011A_02_01]
components.label: Content

components.html: (ii) Please state the financial issue(s) of the substantial shareholder(s). [BQ17011A_02_02]
components.label: Content

components.html: (iii) Has the Licensed Corporation been financially and/ or operationally impacted by the financial stress of the substantial shareholder(s) ? [BQ17011A_02_03]
components.label: Content

components.html: (iv) If the answer is "Yes" in (iii), please state the financial and/ or operational impact to the Licensed Corporation. [BQ17011A_02_04]
components.label: Content

components.html: 3 (a) Does the Licensed Corporation have any recurring operating expenses (eg, staff salary, rental expense) paid on its behalf by group or affiliated companies or other related parties ("Paying Parties") without recharge to the Licensed Corporation (such as in the form of management fee) during the financial year? [BQ17011B_01]
components.label: Content

components.html:
3 (b) If the answer is "Yes" in (a), please state (A) the name(s) the Paying Party(ies), (B) the relationship between the Paying Party(ies) and the Licensed Corporation, (C) whether the Paying Party(ies) is/ are a licensed corporation licensed by the SFC and (D) the CE Number(s) of the Paying Party(ies) which is/ are a licensed corporation licensed by the SFC, of the top 2 Paying Parties ranked by the amount of the respective recurring operating expenses.
(Please choose all options that are applicable to the Licensed Corporation.) [BQ17011B_02]
components.label: Content

components.html: (A) Name(s) of the Paying Party(ies)
components.label: Content

components.html: (B) Relationship between the Paying Party(ies) and the Licensed Corporation
components.label: Content

components.html: (C) Whether the Paying Party(ies) is/ are a licensed corporation licensed by the SFC ?
components.label: Content

components.html: (D) CE Number(s) of the Paying Party(ies) which is/ are a licensed corporation licensed by the SFC
components.label: Content
(iii) Other expenses which exceeds 30% of the total overheads reported by the Licensed Corporation in its profit and loss accounts for the financial year, please specify:

(iv) N/A - the expenses paid by the Paying Party(ies) on behalf of the Licensed Corporation did not fall into any of the cateagories of (i) salary and staff benefits, (ii) office rental or (iii) other expenses which exceeds 30% of the total overheads reported by the Licensed Corporation in its profit and loss accounts for the financial year.

components.html: 3 (c) Is the Licensed Corporation aware of any of its Paying Party(ies) identified in (b) above which is/ are under financial distress (eg, has net liabilities, fails to repay overdue loans or debts, subject to winding-up petition, under receivership) ? [BQ17011B_03]
components.label: Content

components.label: Content

components.label: Content

components.html: II. Remote Booking and Transfer Pricing Arrangements
components.label: Content

components.html: Remote Booking Arrangements
components.label: Content

components.html: 4 (a) Does the Licensed Corporation have in place remote booking arrangements with its group or affiliated companies (ie, Licensed Corporation handling trades or taking positions that are booked to the books and records of its group or affiliated companies ("booking affiliates") or initiating trades to manage risks (eg, entering into hedging positions) of those booking affiliates or vice-versa)? [BQ17012_01]
components.label: Content

components.html: 4 (b) In relation to the trades described in (a), does the Licensed Corporation have the following types of remote booking arrangements in place? [BQ17012_01A]
components.label: Content

questions.label: (i) Risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the booking affiliates risks by the Licensed Corporation would be booked to the books and records of the booking affiliates [BQ17012_01A_01]

(ii) Risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the Licensed Corporations risks by the group or affiliated companies would be booked to the books and records of the Licensed Corporation [BQ17012_01A_02]

components.html:
4 (c) Please indicate the licensing and/ or registration status with financial regulatory bodies of the booking affiliates for booking the risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the booking affiliates risks by the Licensed Corporation.
(Please choose all options that are applicable to the Licensed Corporation.) [BQ17012_02]
components.label: Content
(i) Authorized institutions registered or licensed by the Hong Kong Monetary Authority
(ii) Licensed corporations licensed by the SFC
(iii) Entities registered with or regulated by other financial regulatory bodies (but not registered or licensed by the Hong Kong Monetary Authority or the SFC)
(iv) Entities incorporated in Hong Kong and not regulated by any financial regulatory bodies
(v) Entities incorporated outside Hong Kong and not regulated by any financial regulatory bodies

components.html:
4 (d) Please indicate the role of the Licensed Corporation under the groups remote booking arrangements.
(Please choose all options that are applicable to the Licensed Corporation.) [BQ17012_04]
components.label: Content
(i) The Licensed Corporation would assist in the client account opening process (eg, carrying out know-your-client procedures, customer due diligence procedures)
(ii) The Licensed Corporation would enter into a client agreement with clients
(iii) The Licensed Corporation would service and interact with clients
(iv) The Licensed Corporation would engage in proprietary trading activities
(v) The Licensed Corporation is responsible for risk management of the risk positions taken by Licensed Corporation

components.html: Transfer Pricing Arrangements
components.label: Content

components.html: 5 (a) In respect of the remote booking arrangements as identified in Q.4(a), does the Licensed Corporation have any transfer pricing arrangements in place with its group or affiliated companies? [BQ17012A_01]
components.label: Content

components.html: 5 (b) Does the Licensed Corporation have a written policy or agreement which governs the transfer pricing arrangements between the Licensed Corporation and its group or affiliated companies? [BQ17012A_02]
components.label: Content

components.html: 5 (c) Please indicate if the following statements describe the transfer pricing arrangement in place. [BQ17012A_03]
components.label: Content

components.html: (i) If the answer is "Yes" in Q.4(b)(i),
components.label: Content

questions.label: (A) Trading profit of risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the booking affiliates risks by the Licensed Corporation which are booked to the books and records of its booking affiliates (and the trading profit of other trading entities) would be shared with the Licensed Corporation in part or in full [BQ17012A_03_01]

(B) Trading loss of risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the booking affiliates risks by the Licensed Corporation which are booked to the books and records of its booking affiliates (and the trading loss of other trading entities) would be charged to the Licensed Corporation in part or in full [BQ17012A_03_02]

components.html: (ii) If the answer is "Yes" in Q.4(b)(ii),
components.label: Content

questions.label: (A) Trading profit of risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the Licensed Corporations risks by the group or affiliated companies which are booked to the books and records of the Licensed Corporation would be shared with the group or affiliated companies in part or in full [BQ17012A_04_01]

(B) Trading loss of risk positions taken or trades initiated to hedge the Licensed Corporations risks by the group or affiliated companies which are booked to the books and records of the Licensed Corporation would be charged to the group or affiliated companies in part or in full [BQ17012A_04_02]

components.html: 5 (d) Are there arrangements in place to monitor the trading profit and loss amount transferred to the Licensed Corporation under the transfer pricing arrangements to ensure the financial performance of the Licensed Corporation would not be negatively impacted (eg, the trading loss that can be transferred to the Licensed Corporation for a particular month is capped with reference to the accumulated trading profit and loss transferred to the Licensed Corporation during the financial year)? [BQ17012A_05]
components.label: Content

components.label: Content
